## Decisions made
- Status transitions REJECT invalid moves (409) not silent overwrite —
  withdrawn vs graduated is forensically distinct
- Roster sort: [id-ASC kept, lastName-sort deferred] OR [composite cursor
  done] — fill in whichever you chose
- PII-redaction-as-acceptance-criterion is now the PATTERN for every
  PII-bearing slice (guardians next in slice 5)
- mapUniqueViolation deferral: slice 5 turned out to be a non-trigger.
  Guardian has ZERO unique constraints (phone deliberately shareable),
  StudentGuardian has exactly one — `(studentId, guardianId)` — so a
  local helper `mapStudentGuardianLinkUniqueViolation` discriminating
  `GUARDIAN_ALREADY_LINKED` was sufficient. The multi-constraint
  meta.target fix stays deferred (deferred.md updated) until a slice
  introduces a model with 2+ uniques. SD-pre-check alternative remains
  ruled out.

